{"tid":1965115,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義務律師見證反送中 為抗爭者辯護","createTime":"2020-04-09T09:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T09:24:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"470720b901c7aa48a6f74dc41d7a8c0d9d6361ab","tid":1965115,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"<em>有一種普遍現象。當你看到被拘禁在香港警察局裏的年輕人時，他們會裝作一副很堅強的樣子，在那站著。然後我問，「還好嗎？」他們會說「沒問題」。<br />\n<br />\n然後你再和他們聊個五分鐘，問問他們有沒有得到家人或學校的支持？「你目前心理狀態怎麼樣」？他們就開始哭，每個人都開始哭。有一個年輕人，他竟然問我，「可不可以借你的肩膀？我撐不下去了。」他才17歲，我們就擠在警局的小屋裏互相擁抱著。最後他被保釋出去了。<br />\n<br />\n大約三周前，在旺角道上有個年輕人走過來對我說「我得繼續戰鬥」，就是同一個年輕人。我問他為何仍然要出來，他說「因為很多人都被抓了，所以我得站出來」。</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>~ 黃國桐</em><br />\n<br />\n在過去幾個月裏被逮捕的將近五千名香港抗爭者的命運究竟如何？作為香港抗爭者的義務律師，黃國桐為他們做辯護是怎樣一種經歷？從他的角度，香港警察和政府是如何妨礙司法的？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ERgRwkYILF8&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DERgRwkYILF8%26feature%3Demb_title&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVQTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=af9645ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ERgRwkYILF8&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n文字版<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-04-09/7512348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-04-09%2F7512348&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVQTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=1387e929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-04-09/7512348</a>"},{"pid":"ce8455a7e6f9611dba40f9de66b8eb6214b7b9d2","tid":1965115,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349c809070d1fca6d7bbff16e007ebd6afab9810","tid":1965115,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0